dc_description_s: This raster dataset shows built up areas and land cover in Hungary. This map is generalized from ArcHungary vector layers GeoX Kft. (2020). Land Cover, Hungary, 2022. GeoX Kft. Available at: https://purl.stanford.edu/pg505zb5190 This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
